headline: Shift4 Payments Set to Join the S&P MidCap 400
summary: Shift4 Payments Inc. (NYSE:FOUR) will replace R1 RCM Inc. (NASD:RCM) in the S&P MidCap 400 effective prior to the opening of trading on Wednesday, November 20. TowerBrook Capital Partners and Clayton, Dublier & Rice will acquire R1 RCM in a transaction expected to be completed on or about November 19.

headline: Starbucks (NASDAQ:SBUX) Still Has Room for Improvement Before Buying
summary: “The customer is always right” is a credo that is often used and applies especially to consumer-facing businesses like Starbucks (SBUX).
